tip.text: HAVE TO TRY WHEN IN BUDAPEST!! All flavours are amazing!! Too hard to choose the best!
An open concept cafe that provides unique flavored macarons. Pistachio is the best! Wifi is available too. Best in Budapest!
HAVE TO TRY THEIR PORTOBELLO BURGER AND MILKSHAKE!!!! 👍👍👍
Go early to avoid queuing. Good cup of mocha and food portions are big! 👍

Located in the 7th district, a cool hippie part of Budapest. Soups are unique, raspberry mint drink is very refreshing and portion for sandwich and pasta is big. Friendly staff & relatively affordable
Staff is extremely helpful in recommending and providing great service! The meat starter platter is high recommended!! 👍
Friendly staff! Try the chocolate rolls!!! 👍
